k=2^{m-(n+1)}
a^{2^{n+1}}-1\mid a^{2^m}-1
(a^{2^{n+1}})^{2^{m-(n+1)}} = a^{2^{n+1}.2^{m-(n+1)}} = a^{2^m}
(a^{2^n}+1)(a^{2^n}-1)(a^{2^{n+1}}+1)(a^{2^{n+2}}+1)\cdots(a^{2^{m-1}}+1) = a^{2^m}-1
\rm\ mod\ X+1:\ \ X\equiv -1\ \Rightarrow\ X^{\:2\:K}\equiv 1\:.\ 
